<chapter id="chreftodopane">
  <title>The To-Do Pane</title>

  <sect1>
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para><xref linkend="figreftodooverview"/> shows the To-Do Pane.</para>

    <!-- This should be a comprehensive picture. In fact its just the minimum
         at the moment. It would be good to put some bubbles on this one
         pointing things out as well. -->

    <figure id="figreftodooverview" float="1">
      <title>Overview of the To-Do Pane</title>

      <screenshot><mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata format="GIF" align="center"
                     fileref="images/reference/todooverview.gif"/>
        </imageobject>

        <textobject>
          <para>The ArgoUML To-Do Pane. A rectangular pane, with a bar at the
            top containing from left-to-right, a drop-down selection box
            labelled <literal>By&nbsp;Priority</literal>, a button and a
            yellow highlighted count of items. The body of the Pane shows a
            hierarchy of To-Do items.</para>
        </textobject>
      </mediaobject></screenshot>
    </figure>

    <para>This pane provides access to the advice that comes from the Critics
      processes running within &argouml;.</para>

    <para>A selector box at the allows a choice of how the data is presented,
      a button allows the display of the hierarchy to be changed, and
      there is an indicator the number of To-Do items identified.</para>
  </sect1>

